Abandoned carts remain the silent revenue killer for e-commerce operators. Industry averages hover around 70% abandonment, which means for every $100,000 in potential revenue, $70,000 walks out the digital door. LiveRecover attacks this problem with a controversial approach: real humans sending SMS messages instead of automated sequences.

Our team has deployed LiveRecover across 47 high-AOV storefronts over the past 18 months, ranging from luxury home goods to premium fitness equipment. The results vary dramatically based on product category, price point, and existing recovery infrastructure. This review breaks down exactly when LiveRecover makes financial sense and when you're better served by automated alternatives.

